<title>Who is traveling?</title>
</head>
<body>
<s:form method="post" action="guide!who">
	<h2>Who is traveling?</h2>
	<p>A Travel Authorization request is tied to one person. That person is responsible for collecting the cash advance and filing the expense claim.</p>
	<p>Who is traveling?</p>
	<ul style="list-style-type: none;">
		<li><input type="radio" value="ORIGINATOR" name="travelerType" id="step1_traveler1" /> <label for="step1_traveler1">I am the one traveling</label></li>
		<li><input type="radio" value="OTHER" name="travelerType" id="step1_traveler2" /> <label for="step1_traveler2">Someone else is traveling, I am filing
		the request on behalf of that person</label></li>
	</ul>
	<p>When filing a TA on behalf of someone else, all emails regarding the TA approval will be sent to you, but the person will be able to view the TA on-line.</p>
	<s:submit value="Continue" />
</s:form>
</body>
</html>